 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.521","title":"[audit][cli] Wire subcommand-specific completion options into shell generators","description":"Bounded fresh-eyes audit slice under the audit umbrella. Trace src/cli/completion.rs through cli re-exports and generation call flow, fix the concrete bug where Completable::subcommand_options() is exposed but ignored by generated shell completion scripts, add focused regressions, validate via rch-backed targeted cargo gates, and record the verdict in audit_index.jsonl.","status":"in_progress","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-02T22:57:23.386978162Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-02T22:57:23.386978162Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.521","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-02T22:57:23.386978162Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.522","title":"[audit][cli] Fresh-eyes audit of src/cli/exit.rs","description":"Bounded fresh-eyes audit of src/cli/exit.rs. Trace CLI exit-code mapping through its callers and related error/result types, look for obvious correctness or contract bugs, and record the verdict in audit_index.jsonl. Keep the scope local unless a concrete adjacent defect requires a minimal fix.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"TanStork","estimated_minutes":60,"created_at":"2026-04-02T23:07:45.708971214Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-02T23:24:38.520879006Z","closed_at":"2026-04-02T23:24:38.520519918Z","close_reason":"Completed: fresh-eyes audit of src/cli/exit.rs found that the documented 0..=125 semantic exit-code contract was unenforced across the CLI error/exit flow. Added ExitCode::is_valid/sanitize, sanitized CliError::exit_code(), and sanitized the top-level std::process::exit path in src/bin/asupersync.rs. Validation via rch: cargo check --features cli --all-targets PASS; cargo test --features cli --lib exit_code_builder_sanitizes_invalid_values -- --nocapture PASS; cargo test --features cli --lib sanitize_invalid_exit_codes -- --nocapture PASS after one initial worker disk-space retry. cargo clippy --features cli --all-targets -- -D warnings is still blocked by unrelated pre-existing issues in src/lab/network/harness.rs, src/lab/network/network.rs, and src/cx/wrappers.rs. cargo fmt --check is still blocked by unrelated pre-existing formatting drift in src/cx/wrappers.rs and src/lab/network/harness.rs.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["audit","cli"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.522","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-02T23:07:45.708971214Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
